## Limitations
The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not cover all possible strategies for enhancing creativity. Additionally, the search was restricted to online resources, potentially excluding valuable insights from offline publications. The variability in publication dates also means that some strategies might be more relevant or effective than others in the current educational context.

